DOC.brief_summary: 15 to 20 % of nulliparous needs an induction at term. None study has evaluated Foley catheter induction at home versus expectative in this population
DOC.brief_title: Outpatient Foley Catheter for Induction of Labor in Nulliparous for Prolonged Pregnancy
DOC.criteria: prolonged pregnancy (D+4) nulliparous no complication during pregnancy location near th hospital (20 mn by car) Bishop < 6 medical history small for gestationnal age PROM Live alone
